OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy today across
OL,6,Fnorthern Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fwith some light showers. Dry with
OL,8,Fplenty of warm sunny spells elsewhere.
OL,9,FFeeling very warm in the south with
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy in the north tonight
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of light drizzle in
OL,14,Fplaces. Largely dry elsewhere with
OL,15,Fclear spells and a few fog patches.
OL,16,FShowers possible in East Anglia.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FStaying cloudy and cool in
OL,19,Fthe far north on Wednesday with light
OL,20,Fshowers possible. Dry and sunny
OL,21,Felsewhere with some very warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
